<title>Lotse</title>
<!-- Changed by: Jean-Michel Augusto, 26-Jan-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="/gifs/fond.jpg">

<h1>LOTSE</h1><P>
the pilot through the informationsystems <A HREF="CEOWATiS.html">WATiS</A>.
<P>


The Information resides in a relational Database on the central computer of the <A HREF="http://www.gkss.de/">GKSS</A> research center.<P>
 It contains "hard data" as well as describing data like abstracts, methods and parameters. It is organized in a project-oriented manner, i.e. each project has its own optimal data structure, all projects have in common the meta-information and the relation to the place of measurement or data.
<P>
The full featured LOTSE programm resides on the central computer and is usable via a telnet session (for a limited group only). <P>
For a telnet3270 session  click <A HREF="tn3270://LOTSE on@141.4.4.11/">here</A>.<P>
For standard VT100-telnet click <A HREF="telnet://LOTSE on@141.4.4.21/">here</A>.<P>
Here is some <A HREF="Lotse-help.html">help</A> .<P>
 <HR>

<ADDRESS>October, 1st  1994 - WATiS  at GKSS : watis@gkss.de</ADDRESS>


