    <TITLE>TIS Search</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<!-- Copyright 1996 Trusted Information Systems -->
<!-- Design and programming: The James Gang (e-mail:jgang@jamesgang.com) -->
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#191970" VLINK="#B22222" ALINK="#B22222">
<P><CENTER>
<A HREF="/docs/index.html">
<IMG SRC="/docs/images/tisbanner.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="TIS" WIDTH="378" HEIGHT="27"></A> 
<HR>
<A HREF="/docs/search/index.html">
<IMG SRC="/docs/images/search.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="profile" WIDTH="62" HEIGHT="16"></A> 
</CENTER>
<HR>
<!-- Main Body -->

<FONT SIZE="6">TIS Search</FONT> <BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H2>Using the Search Engine</H2>
You may search the TIS site using either keywords or a concept. To search
by concept, enter a group of words (as you would write or speak them) that
describe the concept. The search will retrieve documents based on the concept
described, even if the document does not contain the exact words in your
query. For example, a search on <B>&quot;downloading Firewall Toolkit&quot;</B>
would list all the pages that included the concept.<BR>

<FORM ACTION="/docs/cgi-bin/AT-completesearch.cgi" METHOD="POST">

<DL>
  <DT><B>Type of search:</B> 
  <DD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="mode" VALUE="simple" CHECKED>Keywords
  <DD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="mode" VALUE="concept">Concept described
in a phrase 
  <DD><BR>
<!--  <DT><B>What to search:</B> 
  <DD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="db" VALUE="complete" CHECKED>Entire TIS site 
  <DD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="db" VALUE="products">Products and Services
  <DD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="db" VALUE="research">Research 
  <DD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="db" VALUE="consulting">Consulting 
  <DD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="db" VALUE="corporate">Corporate -->
</DL>
<B>Enter keywords or concept:</B><BR>
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="search" SIZE="50"><BR>
<BR>
<INPUT TYPE="submit" VALUE="Search"> <INPUT TYPE="reset" VALUE="Clear">
</FORM><p> 
<BR>
Documentation about <A HREF="AT-queryhelp.html">making queries</A> is available.<BR>
If you can't find what you want, please send mail to <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@tis.com">webmaster@tis.com</A>.<BR>
Search engine courtesy of <A HREF="http://www.excite.com/">Excite Inc.</A><BR>
<BR>
You can also search through our site using the <B><A HREF="/docs/search/directory.html">File Directory</A></B>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
