<Font size= 6>Gauntlet&#174; Internet Firewall</font>
<Blockquote>


<Font size = 4><B>Now Available as a Native Windows NT&#174; Application</B></Font>
<p>
This isn't a "hacked" UNIX port!  Our Gauntlet Internet Firewall for Windows NT is specifically 
designed to take full advantage of the features of this popular operating system.  
With Gauntlet Internet Firewall for Windows NT, you'll get:<p>

<UL>
<LI>a superior Windows NT GUI
<LI>support for Windows NT threads
<LI>NT multiprocessor support
<LI>exceptional performance standards
</UL>
<P>
But most of all you get the security expertise that's only available from Trusted Information Systems, Inc.  
TIS is pleased to present this new option in operating systems to help customers choose the Gauntlet Internet 
Firewall that best suits their needs.
