4<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>About TIS</TITLE></HEAD>
<!-- Copyright 1996 Trusted Information Systems -->
<!-- Design and programming: The James Gang (e-mail:jgang@jamesgang.com) -->

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" Link="#191970" VLink="#B22222" ALink="#B22222">

<center>
<a href="/docs/index.html">
<IMG width=378 height=27  SRC="/docs/images/tisbanner.gif" border=0 ALT="TIS"></A>
<HR  size=2 >
<a href="/docs/corporate/index.html">
<IMG width=115 height=16 SRC="/docs/images/cprofile.gif" border=0 ALT="profile"></A>
</center>
<HR  size=2 >

<!-- Main Body -->

<center>

<img width=338 height=48 src="/docs/images/bawotanim.gif">


<BR>
<IMG width=193 height=156  SRC="/docs/images/key.gif" border=0 ALT="TIS keycase">
<BR>
</center>

<Font Size=6>Trusted Information Systems</FONT>

<P><BLOCKQUOTE>
Information on computer systems and networks is critical to the success of businesses and government organizations today.  These organizations depend on information system security to ensure the accuracy, availability, and privacy of
their  information.  Trusted Information Systems, Inc.
(TIS), has been dedicated to providing computer and
communications security solutions for business
information systems for over a decade.
<p>
TIS, a company with a worldwide presence, provides an unparalleled breadth and depth of security expertise. TIS <A HREF="/docs/products">products and services</a> range from theory to practice, and policy to product, with a pragmatic approach. Through a combination of advanced <A HREF="/docs/research">research</a> and engineering, system security analysis, practical and affordable solutions, and training, TIS is transforming the Internet into a safe place to do business.

<HR>
<H3>Security Solutions</H3>

With a thorough understanding of today's technologies,
we have developed and customized computer and
network security products and procedures to meet the
security needs for a variety of computing environments.
To meet the high commercial demand for security over
the Internet, we have developed the <A HREF="/docs/products/fwtk">TIS Internet Firewall
Toolkit</a>.  The firewall software allows system managers
to control access between their corporate networks and
internetworks.  To date, the firewall toolkit has been
requested by over 35,000 Internet users.  We offer a family of
<A HREF="/docs/products/gauntlet">Gauntlet&#174; Internet Firewall</A> 
products, and Gauntlet ForeceField&#153;, a first-of-its-kind product 
designed to protect web servers.  Our patented <A HREF="/docs/products/cke">
RecoverKey&#153;</A> technology was
developed to support effective, exportable, and
recoverable software and hardware cryptography
solutions.  This technology allows software applications
vendors the ability to provide strong data protection
internationally and the end-user the ability to recover
their data when their encryption key is lost, stolen, or
destroyed.<P>

<HR>
<H3>System Security Analysis</H3>

Effective security begins with looking at the whole
computing system and its environment.  Our approach to
securing systems is based on analyzing your system
security in the context of your business requirements and
meeting these needs with practical and affordable
solutions.  <A HREF="/docs/products/consulting/comconslt.html">TIS security analysts</A> are experts at assisting
organizations in defining their systems' security policies
and at conducting risk assessments.<P>

<HR>
<H3>Advanced Research and Engineering</H3>

TIS is internationally renowned for research in information systems security.  We are actively participating in government research contracts and internal research and development projects that advance the state of the art in trusted system technology.  Under <a href="http://www.darpa.mil/"> DARPA</a> and National Laboratory sponsorship, TIS staff are performing innovative research in access control for O/S and networks, cryptography (including key management), security services for Internet mail, trusted distributed file systems, secure distributed operating systems, and integrated Fortezza support.  TIS also provides trusted systems engineering and consulting to a number of major government organizations and DoD programs.
<P>
<HR>
<H3>Awareness and Training</H3>

Security awareness is key to any successful security
program.  TIS conducts <A HREF="/docs/products/consulting/training.html">training courses</A> that instill in
students a practitioner's understanding of the threats,
vulnerabilities, and security solutions available for
protecting their systems and data.  Additionally, we
publish the <A HREF="/docs/products/dsl">Data Security Letter</A><font size=1>tm</font>, a computer and
communications security newsletter focusing on the latest
security research and technology news.
<P>

The successful strategy outlined above has gained TIS the
reputation as an international leader in furthering
information system security.  With offices in the United
States and Europe, we have successfully supported large
corporate clients internationally.  Our staff has provided
security expertise for "Fortune 500" financial, investment,
manufacturing, computer, pharmaceutical, and
communications corporations, as well as government
agencies.

<!-- Next -->

