<HR  size=2 >

<!-- Main Body -->

<Font size= 6>Training Services</font>
<BLOCKQUOTE>

<a href="gicm.html"><H3>Gauntlet Installation, Configuration and Management</H3></a><P>
This fast-paced, two-day class focuses specifically on the installation, configuration, and management of the
Gauntlet® Internet Firewall. It offers an overview of basic firewall design concepts, network configurations, and 
Gauntlet Internet Firewall features and characteristics. There is hands-on training in installation and configuration 
as well as management of the Gauntlet Internet Firewall.<P>

<a href="mns.html"><H3>Managing Network Security
</H3></a><P>

This one-day class will address a variety of topics concerning the security of computer networks and the
 hosts connected to them. We will discuss the trade-offs and costs for different approaches to security, and
 will refer to real-life examples of attacks against corporate networks.<P>	

<H3>Customized Security Training</H3><P>

TIS can develop customized courses to meet your particular needs, with an emphasis on the critical elements 
of your own computing environment. We will work with you to develop a curriculum that meets your particular requirements.
<P>
<h3>On-Site Training</h3><p>
All of the TIS classes can be held at customer sites.  Please call for specific requirements for each course.<p>
<h3>Coming Soon</h3>
Watch for new courses which will be scheduled in early 1997.  These classes will include the following: information security policies and procedures, how to conduct your own information security review, as well as other related topics.<p>
<hr>

