<DOCHDR>
http://shadowplay.hq.tis.com:80/docs/research/tmach/index.html 192.94.214.48 19970120231151 text/html 5873
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Monday, 20-Jan-97 23:09:57 GMT
Server: Open-Market-Secure-WebServer/2.0.0.RC3
MIME-version: 1.0
