<!-- Main Body -->

<Font size= 6> Protect your data, your privacy, and your computer
networks</Font>
<P>
<center>
<IMG width=172 height=170
SRC="/docs/images/slide1.gif" border=0 ALT="demo">
<IMG width=172 height=170
SRC="/docs/images/slide3.gif" border=0 ALT="demo">

</center>
<Blockquote>

<B>In today's internetworked world nothing is secure without a firewall.</B>
These days, speeding and protecting information sent along Internet
or Intranet pathways is critical, and every business manager is looking
for ways to maximize security. Trusted Information Systems' (TIS)
Gauntlet&#174 Internet Firewalls provide strong points of
defense and
controlled, audited access to services - both from within and without
an organization's private network. Thousands of Gauntlet Firewalls
are already in use internationally.
<BR>
<center><a href="http://www.ncsa.com/fpfs/fwindex.html"><IMG SRC="/docs/images/ncsa.gif"></a></center>
<BR>
TIS' Gauntlet Family of Firewall products offers managers the
most secure firewall system available today. The Gauntlet Firewall system
is application proxy-based. By serving as the only connection between outside,
untrusted networks or users and your private, trusted network, a Gauntlet
Firewall uses specific software application gateways and strong user
authentication
to tightly control access and block attacks. Gauntlet Firewalls provide
a network strongpoint where strict enforcement of your security policy
is concentrated.</Blockquote>

