<!-- Main Body -->

<Font size= 5>
Recent Articles  on Encryption, Security and TIS key-recovery technologies:<P>
</FONT>
<P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>

<UL>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.sunspot.net/news/internal/national_world/data/TEL_01A_848403020_53.shtml">
Technology Is Unveiled for Safer Internet Use - Small Maryland Company, 3 Giants Seek to Set Encryption Standards</a>,
by Timothy J. Mullaney, The Baltimore Sun,  November 19, 1996
<P>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.businessweek.com/1996/47/b350287.htm">
Cryptology: Big Breakthrough or Big Brother? Washington may like Key Recovery, but privacy hawks don't</a>,
by John Carey, Businessweek,  November 18, 1996
<P>

<LI><A HREF="/docs/products/cke/info/usmeasures.html">
