EPIC - Electronic Privacy Information Center, Washington, DC USA, July 12, 1996.<P>

<LI><A HREF="/docs/products/cke/info/french.html"> 
As French Hang a Leash on the Net, Military Interests Surface</A>, 
by Jerome Thorel, American Reporter France, Correspondent, June 14, 1996.<P>

<LI><A HREF="/docs/products/cke/info/reno.html"> 
