Comments by Attorney General Janet Reno on plans to establish new agency 
overseeing all digital encryption, and to require
people to register keys with the new agency.<P>

<LI><A HREF="/docs/products/cke/info/newsweek.html">
Newsweek article</A>, June 10, 1996, Business Section, "Scared Bitless", by Steven Levy.<P>

<LI><A HREF="/docs/products/cke/info/ukgovt.html">
DTI Press Release - P/96/430</A> 10 June 1996 - [UK] Government Sets Out Proposals for Encryption on Public
Telecommunications Networks<P>

</UL>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
