<BLOCKQUOTE>



<I>Trusted Information Systems, Inc. (Rockville, Maryland)</I>

<H3>Positions Open in the <A HREF="/docs/products/consulting/comconslt.html">
Commercial Consulting</A> Group</H3>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="NETSECCON"></A>Consultant</H3><P>

	The Commercial Consulting Group at Trusted Information Systems
is seeking flexible, ingenious problem-solvers to fill fulltime
consulting positions. Candidates must write and speak English easily
and well (public speaking and/or training experience is a plus). He or
she should be strongly self-motivated, capable of working independently
in an unstructured environment with a constant learning curve. The
candidate must have commercial business experience, and be
knowledgeable in the full range of Internet technologies, including
TCP/IP, routers, firewalls, and Web servers. Heterogenous networking,
electronic commerce, and host-based security experience is also
desirable.  Expected job tasks include working with prospective
customers, writing statements of work, conducting site visits,
analyzing complex issues and writing extensive reports on deadline.<P>

If you are interested in applying your background to diverse projects
in a small team environment, please send your resume including
education history and relevant course work to: <A HREF="mailto:hrweb@tis.com">
hrweb@tis.com</A> or by FAX to 301-854-5363, or by US Mail to: 
Trusted Information Systems, Inc., 3060 Washington Road (Rt. 97), Glenwood,
MD 21738<P>

