<I>Trusted Information Systems, Inc. (Mountain View, CA)</I>
<BLOCKQUOTE>


<H3>Position Open For A Systems Administrator</H3>
<P>

We are seeking a half time systems administrator for our Mountain View
office.  This individual would administer our Internet Firewall and
our network of UNIX machines, DOS machines and a Mac.<P>

A BS in Computer Science & experience with UNIX is required.  UNIX
system administration, operating system internals, experience with
Mach desirable.<P>

