<I>Trusted Information Systems, Inc. (Los Angeles, CA)</I>
<BLOCKQUOTE>

Trusted Information Systems, Inc. specializes in secure computing

solutions, including the Trusted Mach operating system, secure

real-time distributed computing, network firewalls and network

security, secure mail and other project development efforts.  TIS has

over 150 technical staff members involved in both consulting and

development activities.  This staff is located in offices in Los Angeles,

California, Mountain View, California, Glenwood, Maryland, and London,

England.<P>



