<HEAD><TITLE>Steven B. Lipner</TITLE></HEAD>
<!-- Copyright 1996 Trusted Information Systems -->
<!-- Design and programming: The James Gang (e-mail:jgang@jamesgang.com) -->

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" Link="#191970" VLink="#B22222" ALink="#B22222">

<center>
<a href="/docs/index.html">
<IMG width=378 height=27  SRC="/docs/images/tisbanner.gif" border=0 ALT="TIS"></A>
<HR  size=2 >
Executive Vice President; General Manager, Network Security Products 

</center>
<HR  size=2 >
<!-- Main Body -->
<BR>

<CENTER>
<IMG width=216 height=181 SRC="/docs/images/lipner.gif" border=0 ALT="Steven B. Lipner">
</CENTER>

<Font Size=6>Steven B. Lipner</FONT>
<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>

Steve Lipner is an Executive Vice President of TIS and serves as general manager of its Network Security Product Line.  In this capacity, Mr. Lipner is responsible for all business and technical matters associated with TIS' very successful Gauntlet Firewall family of products.  Since joining TIS in 1994, Mr. Lipner has also worked on and been responsible for commercial and government consulting projects, and research in network security and cryptographic protocols. He has over twenty years of experience as a manager and technologist in computer and network security.  Before joining TIS, Mr. Lipner was Director of Information Systems for the MITRE Corporation (1992-1994) and Engineering Group Manager of the Secure Systems Group at Digital Equipment Corporation (1981-1992).  He was a founding member of the United States National Computer Systems Security and Privacy Advisory Board.  He holds S.B. and S.M. degrees from M.I.T and completed the Program for Management Development at the Harvard Business School.
<P>
E-mail: <a href="mailto:lipner@tis.com">lipner@tis.com</a>

