<HEAD><TITLE>Harvey L. Weiss</TITLE></HEAD>
<!-- Copyright 1996 Trusted Information Systems -->
<!-- Design and programming: The James Gang (e-mail:jgang@jamesgang.com) -->

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" Link="#191970" VLink="#B22222" ALink="#B22222">

<center>
<a href="/docs/index.html">
<IMG width=378 height=27  SRC="/docs/images/tisbanner.gif" border=0 ALT="TIS"></A>
<HR  size=2 >
Executive Vice President, Director and President of the Commercial Division
</center>
<HR  size=2 >
<!-- Main Body -->
<BR>

<CENTER>
<IMG width=216 height=181 SRC="/docs/images/weiss.gif" border=0 ALT="Harvey L. Weiss">
</CENTER>

<Font Size=6>Harvey L. Weiss</FONT>
<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>

Harvey L. Weiss has been a technical professional in the computer
systems industry for over 25 years.  He has been Executive Vice President of
TIS, President of the Commercial Division, and a Director of the Company
since March 1996, and he has been Secretary of the Company since May 1996.
Prior to coming to TIS, he served as President of Public Sector Worldwide
Division for Unisys Corporation, where he developed and oversaw a consulting
and system integration practice that served numerous U.S. and international
government organizations. Before that, he was Vice President of Sales and
President and Chief Operating Officer of Thinking Machines Corporation.
Earlier, Weiss held various senior management positions at Digital Equipment
Corporation.  He holds a B.S. degree in mathematics from the University of
Pittsburgh and is an alumnus of the Program for Senior Executives at the
Massachusetts Institute of  Technology (MIT).
<P>
E-mail: <a href="mailto:weiss@tis.com">weiss@tis.com</a>

