Executive Vice President, Chief Financial Officer
</center>
<HR  size=2 >
<!-- Main Body -->
<BR>

<CENTER>
<IMG width=216 height=181 SRC="/docs/images/kaiser.gif" border=0 ALT="Ronald W. Kaiser">
</CENTER>

<Font Size=6>Ronald W. Kaiser</FONT>
<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>

Ronald W. Kaiser is a TIS Executive Vice President and the company's Chief Financial Officer (CFO).  He has over 20 years experience in public and private accounting and has worked as a top executive in several fast-paced and rapidly growing high-technology companies. He has managed public and private debt and equity offerings, establishment of subsidiaries, mergers and divestitures, and funding for start-up ventures. He has also implemented several information systems and has been responsible human resources functions.  He currently plays a major role in TIS' growth and expansion by ensuring that all financial resources are used to optimum potential while all financial practices are sound.  Mr. Kaiser is a member of the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants (AICPA) and has taught courses on internal control, analytical procedures, and audit planning and strategies for the AICPA and several state accounting societies. He holds Bachelors degrees in both accounting and pre-law from Michigan State University.


<P>
E-mail: <a href="mailto:kaiser@tis.com">kaiser@tis.com</a>

