<HEAD><TITLE>TIS Starts Year With 40,000 Firewalls Downloaded
</TITLE>

<!-- Copyright 1996 Trusted Information Systems -->
<!-- Design and programming: The James Gang (jgang@jamesgang.com) -->
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" Link="#191970" VLink="#B22222" 
ALink="#B22222">

<center>
<a href="/docs/index.html">
<IMG width=378 height=27
SRC="/docs/images/tisbanner.gif" border=0
ALT="TIS"></A>
<HR  size=2 >
<a href="/docs/corporate/press/index.html">
<IMG width=95 height=16
SRC="/docs/images/pr.gif" border=0
ALT="press"></a>
</center>
<HR  size=2 >

<!-- Main Body -->
<table cellpadding = 8>
<TR><TD> <CENTER><IMG SRC="/docs/images/nasdaq.gif" border=0
ALT="NISSC"></A></CENTER></TD>
<TD><Font size= 5>TIS Starts Year With 40,000 Firewalls Downloaded
</Font><br>
<i>Firm Also Welcomes its 75th Gauntlet&#174; Firewall Reseller</i><P>
</td></TR>
</TABLE>

<Blockquote>

Trusted Information Systems (NASDAQ:TISX) began 1997 on a strong note, with

the 40,000th download of its firewall technology and the 75th signing of a

major reseller.  "These numbers confirm TIS's leadership in network security

products," commented Steve Walker, President and CEO of TIS.  "Our goal for

1997 is to continue to dominate in the information security arena, and

reaching these milestones gives us a great start."
<P> 

That the TIS Internet Firewall Toolkit (FWTK) has achieved this magnitude of

use confirms that Trusted Information System sets the standard for firewall

technology worldwide.  In addition to offering the basic toolkit for UNIX

platforms, TIS markets a large family of Gauntlet&#174; firewall products,

including Gauntlet firewalls for Windows NT, Solaris, and HP-UX.  Sales of

Gauntlet Internet Firewalls reflect both new installations and FWTK to

Gauntlet Firewall conversions.<P>

The start of 1997 also marks the attainment of TIS' 75th reseller, with

MATRAnet, a Lagardere Company. The French Internet Service Provider will

market the full Gauntlet Internet Firewall line, with particular emphasis on

the new Gauntlet offerings for the Windows NT and Solaris platforms. <P>

The latest reseller agreement further strengthens TIS' premiere position in

providing security technology to Internet Service Providers, including

UUNET, Compuserve, and Internet Initiative Japan as well as MATRAnet and

more than a dozen major site-focused service providers.  "The TIS reseller

channel is especially strong in Europe and the Pacific Rim," said Harvey

Weiss, President of the TIS Commercial Division.  "We will continue to grow

our international business in 1997, with further activities in these markets

and new efforts in Latin America."<P>

<b>About Trusted Information Systems</b><P>
Trusted Information Systems, Inc., is a leading provider of comprehensive security solutions for protection of computer networks, including global Internet-based systems, internal networks and individual workstations and laptops. The company develops, markets, licenses and supports the Gauntlet family of firewall products and other network security products, and provides cryptography and security consulting training, advanced research and engineering, and services for commercial and government customers. For more information, contact TIS at (301) 527-9500. The TIS home page on the World Wide Web is http://www.tis.com
