<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Directions to TIS Rockville</TITLE></HEAD>
<!-- Copyright 1996 Trusted Information Systems -->
<!-- Design and programming: The James Gang (e-mail:jgang@jamesgang.com) --->

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" Link="#191970" VLink="#B22222" ALink="#B22222">

<center>
<a href="/docs/products/consulting/index.html">
<IMG width=230 height=33  SRC="/docs/images/tisc.gif" border=0 ALT="tis consulting"></A>
<HR  size=2 >
<IMG width=123 height=16  SRC="/docs/images/training.gif" border=0 ALT="Training Services">
</center>

<HR  size=2 >

<!-- Main Body -->
<font size=5>Directions to:</font><p> 
<b>Trusted Information Systems, Inc.</b><br>
15204 Omega Drive, Third Floor<br>
Rockville, Maryland 20850<br>
Phone: 301-527-9500<br>
FAX: 301-527-0482<p>
</center>
<hr>
<p>
<font size=5>From Dulles Airport</font> 
<hr>
<p>

From Dulles Airport, take the Dulles Airport access road east.  Take the 
exit for the Washington Beltway, Rte. 495, towards Baltimore.  Follow Rte. 
495 until it splits into 495 and Rte. 270 North.  Stay in the left lanes 
and follow Rte. 270 North.  Take exit number 8 - Shady Grove Road.  Turn 
left on to Shady Grove Road.  At the second traffic light turn right on to 
Research Blvd..  Follow Research Blvd. and turn left on to Omega Drive and 
immediately turn right into the parking lot for 15204 Omega Drive.<p>
<a href="dllsdir.html">Directions with maps</a>
<p>
<hr>
<font size=5>From BWI Airport:</font>
<hr>
<p>
From BWI Airport, take Interstate 95 South.  Follow Rte. 95 South until in 
connects with the Washington Beltway, Rte. 495.  Take Rte. 495 towards 
Silver Spring.  Take the exit for Rte. 270 North, towards Frederick.  Take 
exit number 8 - Shady Grove Road. Turn left on to Shady Grove Road.  At the 
second traffic light turn right on to Research Blvd..  Follow Research Blvd.
 and turn left on to Omega Drive and immediately turn right into the 
parking lot for 15204 Omega Drive.
<p>
<a href="bwidir.html">Directions with maps</a>

<p>
<hr>
<font size=5>From National Airport:</font>
<hr>
<p>
From National Airport, take the George Washington Parkway North.  Follow 
the parkway until it connects with the Washington Beltway, Rte. 495.  Take 
Rte. 495 towards Baltimore.  Follow Rte. 495, stay in the left lanes and 
follow Rte. 270 North.  Take exit number 8 - Shady Grove Road. Turn left on 
to Shady Grove Road.  At the second traffic light turn right on to Research 
Blvd..  Follow Research Blvd. and turn left on to Omega Drive and 
immediately turn right into the parking lot for 15204 Omega Drive.
<p>
<a href="natdir.html">Directions with maps</a>
<p>
<hr>
