<P><FONT SIZE="6">TIS Internet Firewall Toolkit</FONT>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H3>TIS Firewall Toolkit Download Instructions</H3>
Welcome to the TIS Internet Firewall Toolkit (FWTK) repository. TIS has recently
instituted a registration policy for access to the freely available toolkit.
We have added this additional step to ensure that you are aware that, while
this software is freely available, it is licensed and copyrighted software.
The license agreement is attached.
<P>

After you have read the license, if you agree to abide by its restrictions, 
send a one word -- the word "send" --  e-mail message to <a href="mailto:fwtk-request@tis.com"> 
fwtk-request@tis.com</a>. That is, the single word "send" (with no quotes)
should be in the *body* of the message (not the subject).
An email will be returned to you containing the location of the
FWTK source code and documentation.
<P>
