Trusted Information Systems, Inc., is an employee-owned business
started in 1983, and dedicated to advancing the state of the art
in computer, network,  and communications security. TIS provides
research, consulting, and security products for industry and government,
worldwide.  TIS has significantly accelerated the widespread use
and availability of secure systems. The TIS technical staff includes
internationally recognized experts in computer and network security,
the Internet and internetworking, policy models, operating systems,
trust engineering, and verification.
