<Font size= 6>5. Vendor information</font>


<Blockquote>

<P>
Trusted Information Systems, Inc., is an employee-owned business
started in 1983, and dedicated to advancing the state of the art
in computer, network,  and communications security. TIS provides
research, consulting, and security products for industry and government,
worldwide.  TIS has significantly accelerated the widespread use
and availability of secure systems. The TIS technical staff includes
internationally recognized experts in computer and network security,
the Internet and internetworking, policy models, operating systems,
trust engineering, and verification. 
<P>
Additional TIS products include the Gauntlet PC Extender, PC stack
encryption product and Trusted XENIX&#153;, a B2 rated trusted
operating system.. TIS has offices in Glenwood and Rockville,
Maryland; Tysons Corner, Virginia; Los Angeles and Mountain View,
California; and London, England.
<P>
TIS directly sells and provides security products and services.
TIS also has strategic partnerships and resellers agreements with
over 60 companies, worldwide.
<P>
TIS is a charter member of the National Computer Security Association's
Firewall Product Developers' Consortium, and RSA Data Security
Incorporated's S/WAN Firewall Cryptography Standards Initiative.<P>
