<html>
<head>
   <title>Functional Summary - 13. Product Customer Support</title>

<!-- Copyright 1996 Trusted Information Systems -->
<!-- Design and programming: The James Gang (jgang@jamesgang.com) -->
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" Link="#191970" VLink="#B22222" ALink="#B22222">

<center>
<a href="/docs/products/gauntlet/index.html">
<IMG width=284 height=65  SRC="/docs/images/gtop.gif" border=0 ALT="gauntlet"></A>
<HR  size=2 >
<IMG width=135 height=16  SRC="/docs/images/funct.gif" border=0 ALT="functional summary">
</center>
<HR  size=2 >
<!-- Main Body -->

<Font size= 6><A NAME="13">13. Product customer support
</a></font>
<BLOCKQUote>


<P>
The Gauntlet Internet Firewall is offered with optional problem
resolution support and software update subscription. Also, customers
are added to the Gauntlet Customer e-mail mailing list, will
receive the TIS firewall newsletter, 
which will be available in 1997,  and get discounts on TIS security
training workshops. For more information talk to your Gauntlet
Sales Representative or call Gauntlet Sales at TIS, 1(888)FIREWALL - toll free.
<P>
Gauntlet Authorized Resellers, offer their own product support
to their direct customers.
</BLOCKQUote>

<!-- Menu -->
<Table>
