<DOCHDR>
http://shadowplay.hq.tis.com:80/docs/products/gauntlet/ThinkingFirewalls.html 192.94.214.48 19970120235121 text/html 37510
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Monday, 20-Jan-97 23:49:22 GMT
Server: Open-Market-Secure-WebServer/2.0.0.RC3
