<HR  size=2 >

<!-- Main Body -->
<P>

<Font size= 6>Philosophy of Protection for Triad</font>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<h2>

</h2>
 
The Triad Philosophy of Protection was produced under contract 
to Rome Laboratories under Contract Number F30602-93-C-0235, 
supervised by 
Emilie Siarkiewicz.  The authors, John Sebes, Terry Benzel, Mary 
Bernstein, and Nancy Kelem, wish to acknowledge the contributions 
of the Triad development team, the TMach development team, the 
TMach assurance team, and Manon Levenberg and the administrative 
group in Los Angeles.<P>

