<!-- Main Body -->
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<p>
<h3>APPENDIX D: -  Upgrades in Gauntlet 3.1</h3><p>
-Gauntlet 3.1 is available for HP-UX, SunOs, BSD Unix platforms<p>

-Support for dial-in access, providing a remote dial-in outpost for 
travelling users via PPP or terminal emulation<p>

-User-specific permissions for interactive proxies<p>

-A graphical (HTML) based management interface<p>

-Support for the Post Office Protocol 3 (POP3)<p>

-Proxies added for line printing, real audio<p>

-Authenticated circuit gateway capability<p>
	
