Sun Microsystems Inc.   SunOS 5.4   Generic July 1994<p>

You have mail.<p>

badguy%<p>

<p>

	<i>Expected Results</i>:  If successful, the command prompt (badguy%) 
should appear on hq.peaceful.mil, the computer initiating the rlogin session.<p>

<p>

	<i>Observed Result</i>:  Rlogin session initiation from hq.peaceful.mil 
to badguy.attack.mil through gauntlet.peaceful.mil using transparency was successful.<p>

