<title>NSA Test Report on Gauntlet - Appendix C</title>
</head>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" Link="#191970" VLink="#B22222"
ALink="#B22222">


<center>
<a href="http://www.tis.com/docs/index.html">
