<HTML>
<TITLE>Domain and Type Enforcement</TITLE>

<HEAD>
<CENTER>
<H1>
Domain and Type Enforcement<BR>
Flexible OS Security<P>
</H1>

<FONT SIZE=4>
Lee Badger
</FONT>
[<A HREF="mailto:badger@tis.com">badger@tis.com</A>]

<FONT SIZE=3>
and
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=4>
Daniel F. Sterne
<BR>
</FONT>
[<A HREF="mailto:sterne@tis.com">sterne@tis.com</A>]

</CENTER>
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="intro.idraw">
Domain and Type Enforcement
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="the_problem.idraw">
The Problem
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="the_problem2.idraw">
The Problem (con't)
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="paradigm.idraw">
Using Other Peoples' Software(Safely)
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="partitioned.idraw">
Internal Firewalls
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="access_control.idraw">
Access Control
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="type_enforcement.idraw">
Type Enforcement
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="dan_dte.idraw">
Domain and Type Enforcement (DTE)
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="dtel.idraw">
DTE Language (DTEL)
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="example_pict.idraw">
DTEL Example
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="example.idraw">
DTEL Example
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="network.idraw">
DTE Message Mediation
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="udp_tcp.idraw">
DTE Message Mediation (con't)
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="network_mediation.idraw">
DTE Message Mediation (con't)
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="architecture.idraw">
DTE Prototype Architecture
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="browser.idraw">
Protecting Against Modification or Deletion of Critical Files
</A>(ps)<P>

<LI><A HREF="current_status.idraw">
Current Status
</A>(ps)<P>

</UL>
